text: Sunny Doench (born May 21, 1972, Dayton, Ohio) is an American actress.Variety She was reportedly the original choice to play the title character's sidekick Gabrielle (Xena: Warrior Princess) in Xena: Warrior Princess, but reportedly declined because she did not want to move away from her boyfriend.Sunny Doench's official website She has been married to Nathan John Stricker since August 23, 2014. == Filmography == === Film === {| class="wikitable sortable" |- !
